#: .\modinfo.json .\overmap_terrain.json
msgid "National Guard Camp"
msgstr "国民警卫队营地"

#. ~ Description for National Guard Camp
#: .\modinfo.json
msgid ""
"Gigantic national guard camp filled with military grade enemy robots.  "
"Location is a bit unstable because of it's size so game can heavily lag near"
" it if processing power is relatively low so use it if your computer can "
"process it's size"
msgstr ""
"庞大的国民警卫队营地，充满了军用级别的敌方机器人。由于其规模，位置可能不太稳定，如果处理能力相对较低，游戏在其附近可能会严重卡顿，因此请确保您的计算机能够处理其规模后再使用。"

